"{\"uid\": \"rte.ie-news-2024-0810-1464253-olympics-social-gold\", \"text\": \"  Shauna Burdis  The Paris Olympics are drawing to a close following a spectacular fortnight of sport.  This summer's Games have not only given us a slew of inspiring performances, they have also provided a wave of viral moments.  Watch our video to find out which Olympians have been social media gold over the past fortnight and do not forget to follow @rtenews on TikTok and Instagram.  Video: Shauna Burdis and Philip Bromwell    \\u00a9 RT\\u00c9 2026. RT\\u00c9.ie is the website of Raidi\\u00f3 Teilif\\u00eds \\u00c9ireann, Ireland's National Public Service Media. RT\\u00c9 is not responsible for the content of external internet sites.  Images Courtesy of Getty Images.\"}"